name: Rocket Change
description:
Thank you for playing my short and dumb game. My first time competing at a game jam and I learned a lot. Due my poor time managing and keeping a to do list, I had a lot of wasted time and might have only spent about 10 hours on this of pure doing stuff on unity. You live and learn. <3 At Least I had something to turn in!

Also I hope you like the music (I made it myself)
- @RockCrafts
